#: feedback.py:30
msgid "What did you learn from this? What was missing?"
msgstr "Hvad lærte du af dette? Hvad manglede?"

#: feedback.py:31
msgid "How would you rate this as a learning experience?"
msgstr "Hvordan vil du vurdere dette som en læringserfaring?"

#: feedback.py:33
msgid ""
"Think about the material, and try to synthesize key lessons learned, as well"
" as key gaps in our presentation."
msgstr ""
"Tænk over materialet, og prøv at sammenfatte de vigtigste læringselementer "
"samt de væsentligste mangler i vores præsentation."

#: feedback.py:37
msgid ""
"Take a little bit of time to reflect here. Research shows that a meaningful "
"synthesis will help you better understand and remember material from this "
"course."
msgstr ""
"Tag dig lidt tid til at reflektere her. Forskning viser, at en meningsfuld "
"sammenfatning vil hjælpe dig med bedre at forstå og huske materialet fra "
"dette kursus."

#: feedback.py:43 feedback.py:164
msgid "Excellent"
msgstr "Fremragende"

#: feedback.py:43 feedback.py:165
msgid "Good"
msgstr "Godt"

#: feedback.py:43 feedback.py:166
msgid "Average"
msgstr "Gennemsnitlig"

#: feedback.py:43 feedback.py:167
msgid "Fair"
msgstr "Rimelig"

#: feedback.py:43 feedback.py:168
msgid "Poor"
msgstr "Dårlig"

#: feedback.py:78
msgid "Freeform user prompt"
msgstr "Fri tekst bruger prompt"

#: feedback.py:84 feedback.py:100
msgid "Random number generated for p. -1 if uninitialized"
msgstr "Tilfældigt nummer genereret for p. -1 hvis ikke initialiseret"

#: feedback.py:89
msgid "How user voted. -1 if didn't vote"
msgstr "Hvordan brugeren stemte. -1 hvis ikke stemt"

#: feedback.py:95
msgid "What percent of the time should this show?"
msgstr "Hvor mange procent af tiden skal dette vises?"

#: feedback.py:105
msgid "A list of user votes"
msgstr "En liste over brugerstemmer"

#: feedback.py:109
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "Feedback"

#: feedback.py:112
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Visningsnavn"

#: feedback.py:113
msgid "Provide Feedback"
msgstr "Giv feedback"

#: feedback.py:118 templates/html/studio_view.html:17
msgid "Voting message"
msgstr "Stemningsbesked"

#: feedback.py:119
msgid "Thank you for voting!"
msgstr "Tak for din stemme!"

#: feedback.py:124 templates/html/studio_view.html:25
msgid "Feedback message"
msgstr "Feedback besked"

#: feedback.py:125
msgid "Thank you for your feedback!"
msgstr "Tak for din feedback!"

#: feedback.py:130
msgid "Show aggregate to students"
msgstr "Vis samlet resultat til studerende"

#: feedback.py:159
msgid "Please reflect on this course material"
msgstr "Venligst reflekter over dette kursusmateriale"

#: feedback.py:160
msgid ""
"Please take time to meaningfully reflect on your experience with this course"
" material."
msgstr ""
"Tag venligst tid til meningsfuldt at reflektere over din oplevelse med dette"
" kursusmateriale."

#: feedback.py:163
msgid "Please rate your overall experience"
msgstr "Venligst bedøm din samlede oplevelse"

#: feedback.py:170
msgid "Please take a moment to thoughtfully reflect."
msgstr "Tag et øjeblik til at reflektere grundigt."

#: feedback.py:387
msgid "Please vote!"
msgstr "Stem venligst!"

